  <entry>
    <title>部署TRSS-Yunzai云崽QQNT教程</title>
    <link href="https://zyhqwq.github.io/2024/08/02/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2TRSS-Yunzai%E4%BA%91%E5%B4%BDQQNT%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>https://zyhqwq.github.io/2024/08/02/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2TRSS-Yunzai%E4%BA%91%E5%B4%BDQQNT%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2024-08-02T15:58:09.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-08-05T04:11:44.239Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>今天偶然看到<a href="https://kanna.best/tutorial/trss-yunzai-%E4%BA%91%E5%B4%BD%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88ntqq%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAqq%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/">一篇博客</a>部署了qqnt协议的云崽，这是我也想到qq新版也是qqnt架构，所以我就尝试了去部署，成功了，但…因为被腾讯查封得太狠了，所以大家不要太招摇了</p><h1 id="教程"><a href="#教程" class="headerlink" title="教程"></a>教程</h1><h2 id="注意！！！！！"><a href="#注意！！！！！" class="headerlink" title="注意！！！！！"></a>注意！！！！！</h2><p>我部署的云崽是在我自己家，同局域网下的，并且大佬也说<img src="/images/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%A1%BB%E7%9F%A5.png" alt="登录须知">所以服务器我没有敢尝试，所以我的教程仅供参考，若导致封号本人概不负责！</p><h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><p>Ubuntu x64系统，我试过arm系统是部署不成功的因为chromium浏览器是不支持arm系统的（我真服了，买了个刷好的机顶盒发现不支持）除非您会编译，但我是个小白qwq，只能告诉大家我猜的坑<br>xshell等连接服务器的软件<br>nodejs环境：xu&gt;&#x3D;21版本</p><h3 id="下载安装nodejs"><a href="#下载安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="下载安装nodejs"></a>下载安装nodejs</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v21.7.3/node-v21.7.3-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line">tar -xf node-v21.7.3-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="设置环境变量"><a href="#设置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="设置环境变量"></a>设置环境变量</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line">#在最底下加上</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=/root/node-v21.7.3-linux-x64/bin:$PATH</span><br><span class="line">#注意！！要将“/root/node-v21.7.3-linux-x64/bin”替换为实际路径</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="更新变量"><a href="#更新变量" class="headerlink" title="更新变量"></a>更新变量</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source ~/.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="检验"><a href="#检验" class="headerlink" title="检验"></a>检验</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="下载QQNT"><a href="#下载QQNT" class="headerlink" title="下载QQNT"></a>下载QQNT</h3><p>先下载<a href="https://github.com/LagrangeDev/Lagrange.Core/releases">qqnt</a>，记得点个star<br>偷偷告诉大家，国外机器使用</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/LagrangeDev/Lagrange.Core/releases/download/nightly/Lagrange.OneBot_linux-x64_net8.0_SelfContained.tar.gz </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>国内机器，可以改成</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://githubfast.com/LagrangeDev/Lagrange.Core/releases/download/nightly/Lagrange.OneBot_linux-x64_net8.0_SelfContained.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者(建议但可能更新不及时）<a href="https://www.123pan.com/s/ZiHojv-0chnH.html">点我下载后上传</a>  提取码：l4Ag<br>[备用下载tar.gz](wget <a href="https://github.zyhmifan.top/https://github.com/LagrangeDev/Lagrange.Core/releases/download/nightly/Lagrange.OneBot_linux-x64_net8.0_SelfContained.tar.gz">https://github.zyhmifan.top/https://github.com/LagrangeDev/Lagrange.Core/releases/download/nightly/Lagrange.OneBot_linux-x64_net8.0_SelfContained.tar.gz</a>)<br>是的，加一个fast就可以wget成功了（办法总比困难多）</p><h2 id="解压"><a href="#解压" class="headerlink" title="解压"></a>解压</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -xf Lagrange.OneBot_linux-x64_net8.0_SelfContained.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="提取NTQQ-因为自带的文件夹太多了）"><a href="#提取NTQQ-因为自带的文件夹太多了）" class="headerlink" title="提取NTQQ(因为自带的文件夹太多了）"></a>提取NTQQ(因为自带的文件夹太多了）</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mv /root/Lagrange.OneBot/bin/Release/net8.0/linux-x64/publish/Lagrange.OneBot /root/Lagrange.OneBot</span><br><span class="line">cd /root/Lagrange.OneBot</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x</span><br><span class="line">rm -rf bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="后台运行"><a href="#后台运行" class="headerlink" title="后台运行"></a>后台运行</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">screen -R ntqq</span><br><span class="line">./Lagrange.OneBot</span><br><span class="line">ctrl a+d</span><br><span class="line">#修改appsettings.json中的Port和Suffix，其他不变</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;Port&quot;: 2536,</span><br><span class="line">            &quot;Suffix&quot;: &quot;/OneBotv11&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">#再次进入</span><br><span class="line">screen -ls</span><br><span class="line">screen -r [编号]</span><br><span class="line">回车</span><br><span class="line">扫码</span><br><span class="line">ctrl a+d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="TRSS-Yunzai下载"><a href="#TRSS-Yunzai下载" class="headerlink" title="TRSS-Yunzai下载"></a>TRSS-Yunzai下载</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /root</span><br><span class="line">#下载TRSS-Yunzai</span><br><span class="line">git clone --depth 1 https://githubfast.com/TimeRainStarSky/Yunzai</span><br><span class="line">#切换到yunzai目录</span><br><span class="line">cd Yunzai</span><br><span class="line">#安装</span><br><span class="line">npm i -g pnpm</span><br><span class="line">pnpm i</span><br><span class="line">#安装trss插件</span><br><span class="line">git clone --depth 1 https://Yunzai.TRSS.me plugins/TRSS-Plugin</span><br><span class="line">pnpm i</span><br><span class="line">#安装喵喵插件</span><br><span class="line">// 使用gitee</span><br><span class="line">git clone --depth=1 https://gitee.com/yoimiya-kokomi/miao-plugin.git ./plugins/miao-plugin/</span><br><span class="line">pnpm install -P</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 使用github</span><br><span class="line">git clone --depth=1 https://github.com/yoimiya-kokomi/miao-plugin.git ./plugins/miao-plugin/</span><br><span class="line">pnpm install -P</span><br><span class="line">#后台运行</span><br><span class="line">screen -R yunzai</span><br><span class="line">node app</span><br><span class="line">#再次进入</span><br><span class="line">screen -ls</span><br><span class="line">screen -r [编号]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;今天偶然看到&lt;a href=&quot;https://kanna.best/tutorial/trss-yunzai-%E4%BA%91%E5%B4</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
